{"tid":1782134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以分享下你地覺得香港邊條行人隧道最特別？想影底記錄落黎","createTime":"2019-12-13T16:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T18:21:17.000Z","uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cdfb8a2809a8ceff8e98d789100a86db62dade74","tid":1782134,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:50:39.000Z","msg":"（晚吹） <br />\n<br />\n其實一直都覺得行人隧道<br />\n好似入左去<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">另一個世界</span></span></em></strong>咁<br />\n<br />\n最近突然有想法想記錄底香港既行人隧道<br />\n（用拍照方式）<br />\n<br />\n因為呢次運動連儂場令到18區既隧道或任何公共空間都可以變成現代藝術博物館，除左我地見到好特別既葵涌美術館或大埔連儂隧道，你地有無察覺你個區既隧道<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">好特別無咩人知但每次行過都會時空交錯</span></span></em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLyXkim.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLyXkim.png&h=139f7f86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yd7QFim.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyd7QFim.png&h=535b6816&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gvo4KLH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGvo4KLH.png&h=70b75c55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Ow2wqJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Ow2wqJ.png&h=8a0efaae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"547f80bcf04655f8156249d16e84c5489eeaf50d","tid":1782134,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZhEznyq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhEznyq.png&h=ce76be27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年既資料"},{"pid":"2d5961a5f845062dc65b5c4e106019f54e1d3131","tid":1782134,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T1